    <entry>
      <title>Android原生</title>
      <link href="/2021/10/03/Android%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F/"/>
      <url>/2021/10/03/Android%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一、报错、警告整理"><a href="#一、报错、警告整理" class="headerlink" title="一、报错、警告整理"></a>一、报错、警告整理</h1><h2 id="1、Hardcoded-string-“下一步”-should-use-string-resource"><a href="#1、Hardcoded-string-“下一步”-should-use-string-resource" class="headerlink" title="1、Hardcoded string “下一步”, should use @string resource"></a>1、Hardcoded string “下一步”, should use @string resource</h2><p>以前这种写法是不会报什么错或是警告的：</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Button</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">        <span class="attr">android:id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;@+id/button1&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">        <span class="attr">android:layout_width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;118dp&quot;</span> </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">        <span class="attr">android:layout_height</span>=<span class="string">&quot;wrap_content&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">        <span class="attr">android:text</span>=<span class="string">&quot;下一步&quot;</span> /&gt;</span>&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但是在现在的Android版本好像这不是一个好习惯，应该在res/values/strings.xml中设置：</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;utf-8&quot;?&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">resources</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">string</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;message&quot;</span>&gt;</span>下一步<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">resources</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>引用时使用：</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">android:text=&quot;@string/message&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2、activity页面跳转后是空白"><a href="#2、activity页面跳转后是空白" class="headerlink" title="2、activity页面跳转后是空白"></a>2、activity页面跳转后是空白</h2><p>问题出在系统自动重写的onCreate方法：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">onCreate</span><span class="params">(Bundle savedInstanceState, PersistableBundle persistentState)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">super</span>.onCreate(savedInstanceState, persistentState);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将多出的参数删去，即改为：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">onCreate</span><span class="params">(Bundle savedInstanceState)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">super</span>.onCreate(savedInstanceState);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="二、组件使用"><a href="#二、组件使用" class="headerlink" title="二、组件使用"></a>二、组件使用</h1><h1 id="三、其他内容"><a href="#三、其他内容" class="headerlink" title="三、其他内容"></a>三、其他内容</h1><h2 id="1、如何实现页面跳转后关闭本页面"><a href="#1、如何实现页面跳转后关闭本页面" class="headerlink" title="1、如何实现页面跳转后关闭本页面"></a>1、如何实现页面跳转后关闭本页面</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">onClick</span><span class="params">(View view)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//跳转</span></span><br><span class="line">    startActivity(<span class="keyword">new</span> Intent(MainActivity.<span class="keyword">this</span>, FirstPage.class));</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//关闭</span></span><br><span class="line">    finish();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2、布局中layout-gravity与gravity区别"><a href="#2、布局中layout-gravity与gravity区别" class="headerlink" title="2、布局中layout_gravity与gravity区别"></a>2、布局中layout_gravity与gravity区别</h2><p>gravity是控件自身内容对自己的限定，比如将TextView设置gravity属性：<br><img src="/2021/10/03/Android%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F/image-20211003195120945.png"></p><p>layout_gravity是用来设置该View相对与父View的位置。</p><h2 id="3、ImageView的src和background区别"><a href="#3、ImageView的src和background区别" class="headerlink" title="3、ImageView的src和background区别"></a>3、ImageView的src和background区别</h2><p>background属性即为ImageView设置相应的背景，可以为图片也可以为颜色值。<br>若background设置的是图片，同时宽或高设置为match_parent或者固定值，那么该图片会被拉伸以填满整个ImageView区域。如果宽或高设置为wrap_content，那么图片按照自身大小显示，不会被拉伸。<br>若background设置为颜色值，那么ImageView整个区域都会被该颜色值填充。当ImageView仅仅设置了背景颜色而没有设置src，且宽或者高被设置为wrap_content时，则该View将不会显示。</p><p>src为ImageView设置显示内容，可以为图片也可以为颜色值。设置为颜色值时其表现同background。但是设置为图片时，src属性的表现形式会受到ImageView大小和scaleType属性的共同影响，所以其使用更加灵活。</p>]]></content>
      
      
